<br>
A situation occured where 5 of us were on a mission, and at the end of the mission, a very high dollar item dropped (sellable in game for around 200 million credits, which is a ton of money.)<br>
<br>
To make a long story short, one of my team members looted the item before the roll commensed for the item and then magically went Link Dead.  His friend, who was also on the team, and on the phone with him, told us he wasn't going to come back and that the disk was rightfully his.  Well, after a few moments of words exchange, his friend decided to come back and we wanted to commense the roll for the item...<br>
<br>
Where, here is a log of what happened after he arrived.<br>
<br>
(The thieves in question are Ordit and Flizor)<br>
(I am Trinodast in this conversation)<br>
