<br>
    I have been playing Anarchy Online now for about four (4) months.  Since I have been here, I have had a lot of fun and enjoyed the game.  But last night, something happened to me that I feel is unacceptable.  Last night my team was on a mission, There were five of us total, myself, who goes by the name of Trinodast, Xuum, Cashiz, Ordit and Flizor.  <br>
<br>
   The mission was going well and we were doing well, made it through the mission and finally got to the boss and killed him.  Upon death, on the corpse of the boss was a item by the name of Instruction Disk (Grid Armor MK IV).  Being the team leader, I called the item and told them that we were going to roll on the item, and everyone agreed.<br>
<br>
<br>
   Well, the two who pulled this travesty of theft, Ordit and Flizor, Ordit looted the disk while I was working out all the details of the roll and after he did, he LD'ed.  Well, his friend Ordit, was on the phone with him, told us that he wasn't going to come back and do the roll.  After a few minutes of arguing with his friend, he decided to come back and then agreed to do the roll.<br>
<br>
